{"tid":469790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"戒J日記","createTime":"2017-11-15T16:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T07:08:13.000Z","uid":69978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8119114a3c128764670d2100682dee6a2d71cd0","tid":469790,"uid":69978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:09:13.000Z","msg":"近排發現自己屙尿屙唔哂既感覺<br />\n一晚飲600ml水去成三次廁所(雖然我唔知正唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n個人又瘦唔識生肉<br />\n皮膚冇光澤有幾粒暗瘡咁<br />\n所以想搞返好副偈 個人都自信啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望開呢個post提醒下自己<br />\n每日上黎記錄下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf46ef436944e52e0aa769add9e4bc85f92ce1f","tid":469790,"uid":69978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:12:12.000Z","msg":"15/11/2017<br />\nDay 1<br />\n今日第一日 周圍都望好多正妹 成日都扯到行一行<br />\n好彩都仲忍到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIn trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75543cbdaec38a23b6f240e17d98575743c8a9cb","tid":469790,"uid":69978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"16/11/2017<br />\nDay 2<br />\n今日行左日山 行完返到屋企都攰哂散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係竟然都仲有想打丁既意欲<br />\n當每一次有衝動個時<br />\n我就即刻諗返呢個POST 同自己講你要忍住啊<br />\n發現呢個方法都幾有用<br />\n咁又完左一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e556a3efb38c92891040899accd5ce8784bce0","tid":469790,"uid":69978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T16:19:20.000Z","msg":"18/11/2017<br />\nDay 3<br />\n艱辛既一日終於過去<br />\n今日dayoff留左係屋企 上左一日網<br />\n咁又冇野做 難免會去睇下啲女女架啦<br />\n差小小就破左戒<br />\n三日入面呢日係最難捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望可以堅持到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9f0ce1a36127bbdd74191974b4c0d902d3619e","tid":469790,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T16:26:47.000Z","msg":"作文引人po圖"},{"pid":"225e747f60c34afee82f1c246b0b277f3fbd4760","tid":469790,"uid":69978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:49:36.000Z","msg":"18/11/2017<br />\nDay 4<br />\n唔知係咪因為琴日太多幻想<br />\n今日竟然冇咩衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全冇諗過要打J<br />\n係輕鬆既一天<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c40a9964af16a03337a25f22112ccbec76dba0d","tid":469790,"uid":69978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>作文引人po圖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我呢段時間自己都睇唔少<br />\n影響唔到我既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79858ae94f984da473f7b98054b2921bbd67e33f","tid":469790,"uid":158472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/235628_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F235628_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0283c1ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c22900b5713d8200c0b89dfe6f8ba52b7e3c2b94","tid":469790,"uid":69978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"19/11/2017<br />\nDay 5<br />\n今日又去左行山<br />\n雖然唔係好攰 但係己經習慣左唔打J既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以都冇咩考驗發生<br />\nKeep going!!!"},{"pid":"9ab9f5e20fefcf2c9bd1cf29018f127df4b06f8f","tid":469790,"uid":69978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>19/11/2017<br />\nDay 5<br />\n今日又去左行山<br />\n雖然唔係好攰 但係已經習慣左唔打J既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以都冇咩考驗發生<br />\nKeep going!!!</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a1434024d10552aaa0a81f97a288109f0a4a449f","tid":469790,"uid":69978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:24:12.000Z","msg":"20/11/2017<br />\nDay 1<br />\n今日發生左啲好唔開心既事<br />\n係完全冇打J意欲既情況下打左2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉 當係比啲緩衝期自己啦<br />\n都未試過無啦啦戒咁多日<br />\n諗番起又傷9心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecc00aa933729a21095ba4ac21a76986dea9220","tid":469790,"uid":69978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:10:16.000Z","msg":"21/11/2017<br />\nDay 2<br />\n平談既一日<br />\n冇咩位可以著筆<br />\n好似已經唔會再諗打丁<br />\n唔洗再諗起呢個POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9186b5fbd535933a3fd00d9bb0cff9ff2b617b","tid":469790,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T07:08:13.000Z","msg":"三千人戒丁Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2UMNP_SsDYEJnFfFVw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2UMNP_SsDYEJnFfFVw&d=wRYxnbutjtFT%2FkEIN6DJLC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=4c7749f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2UMNP_SsDYEJnFfFVw</a>"}]}